Name: Cold Water Cowboys
Title: Outwit, Outsmart, Outplay
Desc: Richard Gillett loves the thrill of fishing for herring and the hefty paycheck that comes with it.
LongDescription: Richard Gillett loves the thrill of fishing for herring and the hefty paycheck that comes with it; Paul Tiller looks to beat other boats to his favorite turbot spot; Justin Bridger dreams to take over the family business.
